OL,6,FThe Scottish Child Payment has been
OL,7,Fincreased to #25 and been extended to
OL,8,Finclude eligible children up to age 16.
OL,10,FFirst Minister Nicola Sturgeon has
OL,11,Fcalled the scheme "the most ambitious
OL,12,Fchild poverty reduction measure in the
OL,13,FUK".
OL,15,FSome 400,000 children in Scotland are
OL,16,Fnow thought to be eligible for the
OL,17,Fpayment. The Joseph Rowntree Foundation
OL,18,Fsaid if the scheme was replicated
OL,19,Facross the rest of the UK, 5.3 million
OL,20,Fyoungsters in England, Wales and
OL,21,FNorthern Ireland could benefit.
